<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Error Broadcast - Berani Cerdas</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>body { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); }</style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="w-full max-w-md">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-2xl text-center border border-red-100">
      
      <div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-50 text-red-500 animate-pulse">
        <span class="text-4xl">⚠️</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-black text-slate-900">Terjadi Kesalahan</h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Sistem gagal memproses pengiriman pesan broadcast. Pastikan koneksi database Supabase Anda aktif dan token bot Telegram dikonfigurasi dengan benar di file <code class="bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-xs text-red-600">.env</code>.
      </p>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-purple-700 shadow-md hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
          🏠 Kembali ke Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>